                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable G</hi> 192.) I saw the prisoner running, and I pursued him—I saw him throw the handkerchief from him—I still followed, and took him—he wanted to get down to Saffron-hill—the prosecutor came up and identified him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was at work that evening; I was only liberated from prison on the 17th of June.</p>
